data.description: Mid-Century charm and modern amenities! This updated beauty of a home has both  a covered carport and a paved drive to the basement garage/workshop. And the current owner has made so many updates! New HVAC and ducts on the main floor. Partially finished basement with den, storage, mini split and fireplace. Connected to city sewer and updated plumbing. 2 New Electric Fireplaces. Partially fenced backyard w/ 6 ft wood privacy fence. Updated basement electrical. Stainless steel appliances, granite countertops. New 50 gallon electric hot water heater. Waterproofed basement with transferable warranty. New toilets. New air vents. Updated floor in hall bathroom. New dryer vent line. New ceiling fans in bedrooms and living room. Added shelving in closets. Original mid-century cast iron tub and sink in hall bath refinished. And all in a great location! Please note, per seller, basement garage does not meet NC Code for indoor garage car parking due to need for ventilation and fireproofing.
